      "url": "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:ugcPost:7434368848423923712",
      "text": "Young people need space where they can just build things.\n\nSo we gave it to them.\n\nSix months later, Office 1.14 has helped launch startups that raised over \u00a35M.\n\nWith nothing more than a high bar for talent and an empty office.\n\nI think we\u2019ve stumbled into something much bigger:\n\n\ud83e\udd1d A treatment for the loneliness epidemic\n\ud83d\udc69\u200d\ud83c\udf93 A hack around the graduate jobs crisis\n\ud83e\uddea A lab that actually celebrates risk\n\n\u201cNew ideas must use old buildings.\u201d\n\u2014 Jane Jacobs\n\nThank you Ida Delphine and the Unicorn Mafia for the awesome video \u2764\ufe0f",
